= Features =
//[[SahrisWiki]] Feature List//

* Support for displaying [[BackLinks]], pages that refer to the current page.
* A powerful full-text search engine thanks to [[http://hatta.sheep.art.pl/|Hatta]].
* Supports the creole macro extension and includes a variety of useful [[Macros]].
* Uses the [[http://genshi.edgewall.org/|genshi]] toolkit to make creating new [[Docs/Themes|Theme]] easy.
* Is designed with [[Docs/Performance|Performance]] in mind.
* Breadcrumb navigation support.
* User Authentication (HTTP Auth)
* Flexible Permissions for groups/roles.
* RSS/Atom Feeds
* Edit, Rename, Delete, Upload functionality of content.
* History / Recent Changes

